Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.10,0:01:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰爭的顏色
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.19,0:01:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機翼開始轟鳴的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.66,0:02:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太平無事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.30,0:02:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天因為工作，我會晚些回來\N祝你考試順利——媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.60,0:02:30.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不該是「今天」，應該是「今天也」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.68,0:03:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,池袋…池袋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.07,0:03:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站在那兒的小子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.20,0:03:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在發什麼呆呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.20,0:03:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦，怎麼原來是你啊朝比奈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.41,0:03:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說「怎麼原來是你」太失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.58,0:03:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的跟班呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.79,0:03:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.79,0:03:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.00,0:03:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.42,0:03:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.17,0:03:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有人在盯著我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.80,0:03:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇？是狗仔隊吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.89,0:03:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很受歡迎啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.97,0:03:47.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你呀！！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.18,0:03:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者說…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.89,0:03:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自我感覺良好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.19,0:03:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！討厭！要遲到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.90,0:04:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿，快點吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.57,0:04:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神名君，快點！快點！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.20,0:04:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點！啊，鳥飼！等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.29,0:04:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.08,0:04:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.00,0:04:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最壞的情形是他們可能有過接觸了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.38,0:04:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.54,0:04:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.09,0:04:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上發佈緊急搜索令
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.09,0:04:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.97,0:04:25.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一道防線好像已經被突破了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.47,0:04:29.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碳和氧氣反應生成二氧化碳\N能趕得上嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.27,0:04:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個碳原子和氧氣化合成兩個一氧化碳\N「會不會遲到」這種事想了也沒有用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.52,0:04:35.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.77,0:04:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經這個時候了，你就算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.27,0:04:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「臨陣磨槍，不快也光」吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.57,0:04:42.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你用功是給別人看的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.78,0:04:44.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我猜你就會這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.28,0:04:49.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實連神名君也會有努力的時候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.49,0:04:51.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思啊？！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.16,0:04:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,練習畫畫的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.79,0:04:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.37,0:04:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來指望朝比奈這樣的普通人能夠\N理解這種事情是不可能的了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.00,0:05:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.30,0:05:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浩子，別和綾人搗亂了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.88,0:05:06.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的，男人總是互相護短
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.47,0:05:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.48,0:05:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，實驗中心方面會派其他人去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.06,0:05:19.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.56,0:05:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就按這個指示執行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.19,0:05:22.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼行動
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.98,0:05:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像要調動軍事直升機
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.79,0:05:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿，守！守！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.30,0:05:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝比奈！朝比奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.09,0:05:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神名…君…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.47,0:05:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了，還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.98,0:06:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳥飼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.40,0:06:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿，你沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.70,0:06:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.78,0:06:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳥飼？！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.87,0:06:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照看好守！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.49,0:06:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.50,0:06:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.37,0:06:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就去找人來幫忙…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.08,0:06:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找不到人我就回來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.00,0:06:25.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神名君！神名君！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.98,0:06:42.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？！一個人都沒有？！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.53,0:06:56.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊的平民
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.79,0:06:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真礙事,閃開！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.46,0:07:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍一下！你也是個男人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.30,0:07:53.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的，就這麼點傷…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.69,0:08:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.40,0:08:07.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.49,0:08:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.36,0:08:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饒了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.70,0:08:59.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣我根本找不到人去幫助他們！！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.27,0:09:59.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rah——-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.97,0:10:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.18,0:10:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎！你！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.26,0:10:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站在那裡太危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.19,0:10:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.78,0:10:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美嶼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.53,0:10:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲香…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.30,0:10:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美嶼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.97,0:10:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橙汁可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.39,0:10:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.48,0:10:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總算緩過勁來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.69,0:10:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是戰爭嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.06,0:10:55.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，是戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.49,0:10:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是，很意外啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.70,0:11:02.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到會在這裡遇到你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.37,0:11:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.20,0:11:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為神名君這麼突然地出現
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.66,0:11:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了，無論如何，還算不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.17,0:11:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人總比一個人強
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.00,0:11:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.29,0:11:15.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.46,0:11:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.97,0:11:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你會在那個地方呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.38,0:11:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，難道你也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.47,0:11:27.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美嶼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.89,0:11:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美嶼！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.02,0:11:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在出去還很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.40,0:11:35.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美嶼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.57,0:11:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌聲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.19,0:11:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌聲？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.19,0:11:39.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Dolem
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.19,0:11:39.07,*note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Dolem：MU的人型兵器，又被稱為D-1
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.20,0:11:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡的入侵者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.49,0:11:46.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神名君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.58,0:11:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他還好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.08,0:11:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不必為他擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.87,0:11:50.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理由呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.29,0:11:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺…大概…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.17,0:11:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉，我真是個笨蛋，竟然會問你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.29,0:12:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它在消滅敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.29,0:12:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說那是防衛軍的秘密武器吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.17,0:12:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神名君！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.96,0:12:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，這裡的確很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.97,0:12:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們動用了「那個」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.89,0:12:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.68,0:12:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被稱為首都防衛的核心的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.56,0:12:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.19,0:12:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,bingo！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.70,0:13:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣妥當嗎？動用Allegretto？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.70,0:13:08.28,*note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Allegretto：音樂名詞，指「小塊板」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.28,0:13:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它那方面不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.58,0:13:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有olin它無法覺醒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.58,0:13:12.58,*note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}olin：那瓦克神話名詞，這裡指RahXephon的駕駛員
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.58,0:13:13.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使覺醒了，也無法歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.79,0:13:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現olin
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.57,0:13:42.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美嶼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.07,0:13:44.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美嶼！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.36,0:13:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是神名 綾人君吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.78,0:13:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.57,0:13:48.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.53,0:13:50.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是政府派來的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.58,0:13:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,政府？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.99,0:13:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們沒有更多的時間解釋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.08,0:13:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能跟我們走一趟嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.29,0:13:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.00,0:13:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.29,0:13:59.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.67,0:14:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿！等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.17,0:14:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少要給我個解釋…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.76,0:14:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要太頑固了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.38,0:14:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見囉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.88,0:14:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.59,0:14:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.59,0:14:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以算是正義的使者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.97,0:14:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.47,0:14:57.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，我救了你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.48,0:15:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少該說聲「謝謝」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.49,0:15:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.70,0:15:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在危險之中救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.36,0:15:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.78,0:15:16.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.66,0:15:21.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「為什麼他們的血是藍色的？」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.00,0:15:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很在意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.59,0:15:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會告訴你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.38,0:15:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你跟我來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.38,0:15:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍色血的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.77,0:15:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個世界的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.27,0:15:42.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.69,0:15:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對年長的女性沒興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.98,0:15:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓女性蒙羞可不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.57,0:15:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什公正義的使者！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.78,0:15:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了，行了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.49,0:15:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.38,0:16:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等，綾人君！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.66,0:16:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在發車
