Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.54,0:16:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會保護你的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.05,0:16:51.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對會保護美嶼你的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.88,0:16:52.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
