Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.53,0:19:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卵？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.68,0:19:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡的Dolem！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.09,0:20:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rah——
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.22,0:20:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺醒吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.62,0:20:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾人！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.93,0:20:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快覺醒吧！
